---
// Hero section with guild name and main call-to-action
---

<section id="inicio" class="section relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/90 via-black/70 to-black/90"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 z-10 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-yellow-400 to-amber-600">
        Dominion Guild
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-normal/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Una hermandad dedicada a la excelencia en World of Warcraft. Únete a nuestra comunidad de jugadores apasionados.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a 
          href="#rooster" 
          class="px-8 py-3 bg-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/20 border border-primary/30 text-primary rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          Ver Rooster
        </a>
        <a 
          href="#raids" 
          class="px-8 py-3 bg-transparent hover:bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 text-primary rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          Próximas Raids
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
